|default=}}</includeonly><noinclude>This template is used on Item pages in combination with [[Template:LootDrop]] on NPC pages. Without it, it cannot function.

LootDrop is used on NPC pages to list item drops, recording each drop in the Cargo table <code>loot_drops</code>.

This template queries Cargo to dynamically fetch and link to all NPC pages recorded by LootDrop.
